import React from "react";
import { Text, TouchableOpacity, View } from "react-native";
import { faGear, faBookmark, faBell, faHeart } from "@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons";
import { FontAwesomeIcon } from "@fortawesome/react-native-fontawesome";

const Profile : React.FC = () => {
    return (
        <View>
            <View>
                <Text>Hồ sơ</Text>
                <FontAwesomeIcon icon = {faGear}/>
            </View>

            <View>
                <View>
                    <Text>B</Text>
                </View>

                <View>
                    <Text>Bad liar</Text>
                    <Text>Thành viên cộng đồng</Text>
                    <TouchableOpacity>
                        <Text>Sửa hồ sơ</Text>
                    </TouchableOpacity>
                </View>
            </View>

            <View>
                <TouchableOpacity>
                    <FontAwesomeIcon icon = {faBookmark}/>
                    <Text>Đã lưu</Text>
                </TouchableOpacity>

                <TouchableOpacity>
                    <FontAwesomeIcon icon = {faHeart}/>
                    <Text>Đã thích</Text>
                </TouchableOpacity>

                <TouchableOpacity>
                    <FontAwesomeIcon icon = {faBell}/>
                    <Text>Thông báo</Text>
                </TouchableOpacity>
            </View>
        </View>
    )
};

export default Profile;
